## Confirmed Case
Meets case definition (see Section A for diagnostic criteria) with a recognized risk factor for iatrogenic transmission
(see Box 3)
## Probable Case
- Progressive predominant cerebellar syndrome in a recipient of cadaverically derived human pituitary growth hormone
OR
- Probable CJD (see Section A for diagnostic criteria) with a recognized risk factor for iatrogenic transmission (see Box 3)
Box 3
